{"tid":2437149,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"一千日本師奶票選最快離婚夫婦 前田敦子大勝佐佐木希","createTime":"2021-03-07T16:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T16:33:13.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"46d6804eb67e0799b894a0955d60e0d4ccfc7b19","tid":2437149,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-xgPwT8WMZwP8hgdbRw_0txCOQQ=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6VI7US4TLFEUPMCWVZHX5QWABI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-xgPwT8WMZwP8hgdbRw_0txCOQQ%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6VI7US4TLFEUPMCWVZHX5QWABI.jpg&h=e83afe01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本女子組合AKB48的29歲前一姐前田敦子，傳出與34歲男星勝地涼正辦理離婚，兩年半婚姻簡直凍過水！<br />\n<br />\n日本雜誌《週刊女性》最近向1,000名主婦進行民意調查，由一班睇開八卦新聞的師奶們投下神聖一票，選出十大有婚姻危機的名人夫妻，前田敦子與勝地涼一直被指婚變，更傳出家暴消息，令二人得票最多，以130票獲得冠軍。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/J44aESXv4uxLKYt5_-_xMoYboUc=/802x1052/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SCK557U3IRDQZMK6URIUGVCO6A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJ44aESXv4uxLKYt5_-_xMoYboUc%3D%2F802x1052%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSCK557U3IRDQZMK6URIUGVCO6A.jpg&h=8e808220&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wYUx5vN7JZ3uTIBCoxvd0RKLtfo=/802x800/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZRLACFKNTBF5BF4ID7VVITIL2U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwYUx5vN7JZ3uTIBCoxvd0RKLtfo%3D%2F802x800%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZRLACFKNTBF5BF4ID7VVITIL2U.jpg&h=d5911fe7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n排在第二名是佐佐木希和渡部建，由於男方去年爆出在傷健人士廁格內偷食，更有多位性伴侶，但希妹為了年幼兒子才原諒老公，渡部建事後開記者會道歉及否認性上癮，更一度在東京豐洲魚市場兼職搬海鮮，試圖以苦肉計來博同情，可借至今仍復出無望，在今次選舉中還有97票，僅次於冠軍的前田敦子和勝地涼。第三位是老牌男星石田純一和東尾理子，共有89票，險勝87票、排在第四位的小倉優子與其牙醫丈夫島弘光。<br />\n<br />\n其他打入十大的圈中夫妻還有永山瑛太與木村Kaela，以79票佔第五位，而鈴木保奈美和石橋貴明、木村拓哉和工藤靜香、北川景子與DAIGO，就分別排在第七、第九及第十位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210307/RD2XPQO4YFD3PKXIUBW2AON5TM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210307%2FRD2XPQO4YFD3PKXIUBW2AON5TM%2F&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058jrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=b504336c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210307%2FRD2XPQO4YFD3PKXIUBW2AON5TM%2F&h=ebf0117c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210307/RD2XPQO4YFD3PKXIUBW2AON5TM/</a>"},{"pid":"4f8f4bf930d0969e179de8e35f1c47144f243248","tid":2437149,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:21:28.000Z","msg":"最快分手情侶有無彩同紋身師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f30e4e878a9c34e89039bc8c440f125cc86423","tid":2437149,"uid":96941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:22:14.000Z","msg":"我可以接收佐佐木希"},{"pid":"1930a197f2fb52c31d86b54e991beadc1ce0b6a0","tid":2437149,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f8f4bf930d0969e179de8e35f1c47144f243248","tid":2437149,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:21:28.000Z","msg":"最快分手情侶有無彩同紋身師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:28:23.000Z","msg":"是旦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8031de32dc64bd38a761d2473d268d6349bbbdd8","tid":2437149,"uid":258903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T16:33:13.000Z","msg":"木村都入前10?<br />\n都崩壞左咁多年<br />\n